    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Accused of being a conspirator,\nCharles Brown, who is said to have\nkept an office at Hillyard where\n1. w. w. recruits were enlisted,\nwas arrested last night by Deputy\nSheriff Logan and Captain of De-\ntectives Burns. The keeping open\nof an office for the purpose of\nmaking converts into the |. w. W..\nfaith was explained by Captain\nBurns as an act of conspiracy\nagainst the city of Spokane."
